*   **Decision**: The `oscore-gm-admin-notification` draft will be split after IETF 116. The current draft (Doc1) will proceed with CoRAL content removed. A new WG document (Doc2) focusing on CoRAL usage will be adopted.
*   **Decision**: The March interim meeting, scheduled the week before IETF 116, is cancelled.
*   **Action Item**: Marco Tiloca to submit a revised version of the "Revoke Token Notification" draft incorporating all updates before the cutoff date.
*   **Action Item**: Marco Tiloca to submit a revised version of the "OSCORE Group Manager Admin Notification" draft incorporating as many updates as possible before the cutoff date.
*   **Action Item**: Sigrun Erlingsdottir to submit a new version of the "CoAP Key Group Com over OSCORE" draft by the cutoff date, reflecting the discussed clarifications and updates, including Marco Tiloca as an author.
*   **Action Item**: Rikard Höglund to submit the shepherd write-up and shepherd review for the ACE Key Group Com draft by Wednesday.
*   **Action Item**: Daniel to follow up on the publication request for the Key Group Com draft after Rikard's review is addressed.

